(500079,2,'▶SpringBoot后端视图 - 基于Thymeleaf视图解析','英文官方文档3.0 http://www.thymeleaf.org/doc/tutorials/3.0/usingthymeleaf.html https://github.com/realpdai/tech-pdai-spring-demos https://blog.csdn.net/u012441595/article/details/100022922 原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/spring/springboot/springboot-x-view-thyme...','# ▶SpringBoot后端视图 - 基于Thymeleaf视图解析\n\n> TBD\n\n- ▶SpringBoot后端视图 - 基于Thymeleaf视图解析知识准备什么是模板引擎什么是Thymeleaf实现案例简单的Hello World案例Thymeleaf各种语法案例Thymeleaf增删查改应用案例进一步理解为什么SpringBoot中默认的后端模板引擎会是Thymeleaf？Thymeleaf的生态？Thymeleaf其它常见问题？示例源码\n\n## 知识准备\n\n> 在使用之前需要理解SpringMVC的处理流程，模板引擎，以及Thymeleaf简介等。@pdai\n\n### 什么是模板引擎\n\n### 什么是Thymeleaf\n\n英文官方文档3.0 http://www.thymeleaf.org/doc/tutorials/3.0/usingthymeleaf.html\n\n## 实现案例\n\n> 这里我们通过三个案例来向你介绍Thymeleaf的用法，分别是最基础的Hello World，Thymeleaf各种语法案例和Thymeleaf增删查改应用案例。@pdai\n\n### 简单的Hello World案例\n\n### Thymeleaf各种语法案例\n\n![图片](/api/uploads/files/pdai/Thymeleaf3-250f9aeae8.png)\n\n### Thymeleaf增删查改应用案例\n\n## 进一步理解\n\n> 我们通过如下问题进一步理解Thymeleaf。@pdai\n\n### 为什么SpringBoot中默认的后端模板引擎会是Thymeleaf？\n\n### Thymeleaf的生态？\n\n### Thymeleaf其它常见问题？\n\n## 示例源码\n\nhttps://github.com/realpdai/tech-pdai-spring-demos\n\nhttps://blog.csdn.net/u012441595/article/details/100022922\n\n---\n\n原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/spring/springboot/springboot-x-view-thymeleaf.html','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607798748738-b15c40d33d57?w=800','SpringBoot 2.5.x系列',NULL,0,NULL,'pdai-spring-springboot-springboot-x-view-thymeleaf','▶SpringBoot后端视图 - 基于Thymeleaf视图解析 - 技术博客','英文官方文档3.0 http://www.thymeleaf.org/doc/tutorials/3.0/usingthymeleaf.html https://github.com/realpdai/tech-pdai-spring-de...',0,'PUBLISHED',3453,345,10,46,'2025-11-06 00:00:00','2025-11-06 00:00:00','2026-05-08 23:34:42',NULL,0) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `author_id`=VALUES(`author_id`),`title`=VALUES(`title`),`summary`=VALUES(`summary`),`content`=VALUES(`content`),`cover_url`=VALUES(`cover_url`),`category`=VALUES(`category`),`offline_reason`=VALUES(`offline_reason`),`featured`=VALUES(`featured`),`featured_at`=VALUES(`featured_at`),`seo_title`=VALUES(`seo_title`),`seo_description`=VALUES(`seo_description`),`warn_flag`=VALUES(`warn_flag`),`status`=VALUES(`status`),`view_count`=VALUES(`view_count`),`like_count`=VALUES(`like_count`),`favorite_count`=VALUES(`favorite_count`),`comment_count`=VALUES(`comment_count`),`published_at`=VALUES(`published_at`),`updated_at`=VALUES(`updated_at`),`deleted_at`=NULL;
